        {
          "id": "s_faq_01",
          "type": "faq",
          "props": {
            "heading": "Frequently Asked Questions",
            "subheading": "Got questions? We have answers. Can't find what you're looking for? Chat with our team.",
            "q1": "Do I need to know how to code?",
            "a1": "Absolutely not. PageCraft is built for everyone — from complete beginners to experienced developers. Our visual editor lets you drag, drop, and customise without touching a single line of code.",
            "q2": "Can I use my own domain name?",
            "a2": "Yes! With any paid plan, you can connect your own custom domain (e.g. yourbrand.com). We provide step-by-step instructions, and our support team is always here to help with the setup.",
            "q3": "What happens to my site if I cancel?",
            "a3": "You keep full ownership of your content. Before cancelling, you can export your entire website as clean HTML/CSS files that you can host anywhere — forever.",
            "q4": "Is there a free plan?",
            "a4": "Yes! Our free plan lets you build up to 3 pages with a PageCraft subdomain. It's a great way to try everything before upgrading. No credit card required to start.",
            "q5": "How does the AI content generator work?",
            "a5": "Our AI uses Groq's Llama model to generate headlines, descriptions, and CTAs based on your section type and tone preference. It's free to use with your own Groq API key.",
            "q6": "Can I export my site?",
            "a6": "Absolutely. Export as clean HTML (single file or multi-page ZIP), React JSX components, or a JSON project backup. Your code is production-ready and fully portable.",
            "bgColor": "#ffffff",
            "textColor": "#0f172a",
            "accentColor": "#f59e0b"
          }
        },
