            "subheading": "A team of builders, for builders",
            "body": "PageCraft was founded in 2023 by a small team of designers and engineers who were tired of choosing between ease-of-use and power.\n\nWe built PageCraft to be both — a tool you can pick up in minutes, yet powerful enough to build any website you can imagine.\n\nToday our team of 12 works remotely across 6 countries, united by the belief that great tools should be accessible to everyone.",
